<DOCNO> AP880728-0120 </DOCNO>
<FILEID>AP-NR-07-28-88 1312EDT</FILEID>
<1ST_LINE>r i AM-BRF--BabySacrificed     07-28 0098</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>AM-BRF--Baby Sacrificed,0100</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>Mother Charged With Murdering Baby Dreamed Of Riches</HEAD>
<DATELINE>DHAKA, Bangladesh (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A woman who has been accused of killing
her only child with a butcher knife dreamt she would become rich if
she conducted such a sacrifice, a newspaper reported Thursday.
   Shahida Khatun, 32, was charged with murdering her 4-month-old
baby in southern Pirojpur district on Sunday. If convicted, Mrs.
Khatun could received up to 14 years in prison, according to The
New Nation newspaper.
   The English-language paper quoted police officials as saying the
woman attacked her child after waking from the dream.
</TEXT>
