<HEAD>Campbell Named Vice President's Convention Floor Leader</HEAD>
<DATELINE>COLUMBIA, S.C. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Gov. Carroll Campbell of South Carolina
will be floor manager for Vice President George Bush at next
