<2ND_LINE>PM-Wall Street 2pm,0442</2ND_LINE>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The stock market gained ground today after a
tentative opening as investors picked up blue chip and high-tech
